# Intuition
<!-- DeI scribe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
I need to swap left and right indices and keep on doing it until they both collide 
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Copy all the values in vector , swap left and right and keep on doing it until left!=right
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(n)
- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
