## Logic
- This is one of the *standard* question in Single Linked List.
- I have solved it using ***three pointer approach*** which is *inplace* and fast.

## Implementation
```
ListNode* reverseBetween(ListNode *head, int left, int right)
        {
		//The three pointers here are prev , curr and forw
            ListNode *temp = new ListNode(0);
			//A dummy node before head
            temp->next = head;
            ListNode *prev = temp;	

            for (int i = 0; i < left - 1; i++)
                prev = prev->next;
            ListNode *curr = prev->next;

            for (int i = 0; i < right - left; i++)
            {
                ListNode *forw = curr->next;	
                curr->next = forw->next;
                forw->next = prev->next;
                prev->next = forw;
            }
            return temp->next;
        }
```

