**Approch 2:** Application of [LCS](https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-common-subsequence/)
-> just find LCS and check if its equal to s.length() then s is subsequence of t
**CODE:**
```
public int isSubsequence(String s,String t){
   int lcs=LCS(s,t);
   return lcs==s.length();
}

private int LCS(String text1, String text2) {
        int[][] dp=new int[text1.length()+1][text2.length()+1];

        for(int i=1;i<dp.length;i++){
            for(int j=1;j<dp[0].length;j++){
                if(text1.charAt(i-1)==text2.charAt(j-1)){
                    dp[i][j]=1+dp[i-1][j-1];
                }else{
                    dp[i][j]=Math.max(dp[i-1][j],dp[i][j-1]);
                }
            }
        }
        return dp[text1.length()][text2.length()];
    }
```	
