* ### **DP SOLUTION: BOTTOM-UP or TABULATION (Accepted)` [NAIVE SOLUTION]`**
* **Runtime : 40ms**
*  **PREREQUISITE : `LONGEST COMMON SUBSEQUENCE (LCS)`**
```
class Solution {
public:
    bool isSubsequence(string s, string t) {
        int n = s.size(), m = t.size();
        vector<vector<int>> dp(n + 1, vector<int>(m + 1, 0));
        for(int i = 1; i <= n; ++i){
            for(int j = 1; j <= m; ++j){
                if(s[i - 1] == t[j - 1])
                    dp[i][j] = 1 + dp[i - 1][j - 1];
                else
                    dp[i][j] = max(dp[i - 1][j], dp[i][j - 1]);
            }
        }
        int lcslen = dp[n][m];
        return lcslen == n? true : false;
    }
};
```
